{"tid":1045354,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中國網易 Overwatch 電競戰隊終獲勝！42 場敗仗破盡聯賽連敗世界紀錄","createTime":"2019-03-03T14:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T12:19:25.000Z","uid":51464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ded76bd2c9c718be0f0f34715cb8baab0a142fe3","tid":1045354,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"Blizzard（暴雪娛樂）旗下的 Overwatch League 電競聯賽，已在 2 月 15 日起正式開季。本季聯賽隊伍數目，由上一季的 12 隊增至 20 隊，預期競爭會變得更為激烈。另外，網易旗下的 Shanghai Dragons（上海龍之隊），在 2018 賽季中所有聯賽賽事均獲敗積，創下了連敗 40 場的紀錄。Shanghai Dragons 到底能否在 2019 年賽季中，盡早獲得首場勝仗，也成為了觀眾關注的焦點之一。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2283381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2283381&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4c2ac0ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2283381</a><br />\n==================================================<br />\n中國電競零的突破！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925018313837b7ab5d90bf4b6008f98fb4c32d18","tid":1045354,"uid":121697,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ded76bd2c9c718be0f0f34715cb8baab0a142fe3","tid":1045354,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"Blizzard（暴雪娛樂）旗下的 Overwatch League 電競聯賽，已在 2 月 15 日起正式開季。本季聯賽隊伍數目，由上一季的 12 隊增至 20 隊，預期競爭會變得更為激烈。另外，網易旗下的 Shanghai Dragons（上海龍之隊），在 2018 賽季中所有聯賽賽事均獲敗積，創下了連敗 40 場的紀錄。Shanghai Dragons 到底能否在 2019 年賽季中，盡早獲得首場勝仗，也成為了觀眾關注的焦點之一。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2283381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2283381&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv96RZRvdwXM7zdV